text: Hay Nabi! tharoang ka ko manga karomang ka, go so manga wata a ka a manga babay, go so manga babay ko miyamaratiyaya, a sapngn iran ko manga olo iran go sii ko manga paras iran so manga nditarn iran go so manga sapng iran, ka an kadilongi so manga paras iran ago so manga rarb iran ago so manga olo iran. Giyoto man i lbi a marani a kakilala a kiran, na di siran maziyanta. Na tatap a so Allah na Manapi, a Makalimoon
